My Foundation, @jawsyouthplaybook partners with @PPFCA to host our Second Annual Prom Drive. 

The expense of prom stops many teens from attending their dance. This is why my foundation and PPFCA stepped in to support each girl by being personally styled with a dress of their dreams, jewelry, shoes, and a purse. 

The genuine smiles from volunteers, parents, and girls are why events like these are unforgettable. I’d like to thank everyone who donated dresses, shoes, and jewelry to this event. A very special thanks to my friends at @NFLFilms, @cosmocares @cdenicola , @EaglesCheer, PPFA, and the CEO Group!

Earlier this week, my world was shattered as I received the devastating news of the sudden passing of my dear friend and business manager, Jason "Coffee" Jones. The pain and sorrow I feel are indescribable, as I try to come to terms with the unimaginable loss of someone who has been an integral part of my life for almost 10 years.
 
Jason, you were more than just a colleague and my right-hand-man; you were family. We shared a bond that went far beyond our professional relationship. Your dedication and tireless work ethic were unmatched, and I am forever grateful for the support and kindness you showed my family and me.
 
Your impact on my life and the lives of those around you will never be forgotten. Thank you for being my friend and my brother. You will always hold a special place in my heart.

I can feel the excitement building up inside me! The Jaws Bike Drive, presented by @mallchevy, is just around the corner! 

It's heartbreaking to think that many at-risk youth may never experience the joy of getting their first bike due to financial struggles. That's why I'm reaching out to you for help. Let's spread some Christmas cheer by giving the gift of a bike, lock, and helmet to these deserving kids in our area. Your generosity can make a world of difference in their lives.

Head to https://fundraise.givesmart.com/e/MII-rA?vid=12aj4y to buy a Child a Bike!

We are giving away over 400 bikes for The Holidays.
Thank you sponsors!
My Foundation is committed to helping Kids and putting a smile on their faces! 🎅 Santa Jaws

Time to give away to the all the  smiling faces. This years 🚲 Bike drive presented by @mallchevy Thank for all your donations.  @jawsyouthplaybook was able to give away 💯’s off bikes, locks & helmets to children. BIG Thank you to all the volunteers, donors, sponsors and the team who made this all possible. 🙏❤️🎅
